# Functor Lang sources and the functor-lang crate's golden files
# (.ast/.ir/.run/.trace/.check) are byte-compared against LF-rendered output
# in tests — never CRLF-normalize them on checkout, or the goldens diverge on Windows.
*.fun text eol=lf
*.ast text eol=lf
*.check text eol=lf
*.ir text eol=lf
*.run text eol=lf
*.trace text eol=lf
